    "## Results"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "Exploratory analysis showed an approximate 1% correclation between the predictor variables being analysed and accident severity.\n",
    "The negative correlation figure shown for road conditions is expected as a result of the inversely coded variables mentioned above. \n",
    "The logistic regression model indicated statistical significance after completion of the train test method.\n",
    "In order to evaluate the model, the acuracy of the classifier was measured using the Jaccard index. This yielded a result of .675, signifying satisfactory results.\n",
    "Further evaluation of the ML model showed a log loss of .63 which is indicative of a slight uncertainty in the model created.\n",
    "\n"
